data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS, PLEASE SUBMIT HIGHEST & BEST BY 12/14/23....Uncover the potential in this tranquil 4 BR oasis! Step into the ideal family starter home, where space, comfort and outdoor leisure unite. Picture yourself in this charming 4-bedroom 2 bath haven in a serene neighborhood.  A little TLC can transform it into your dream residence.  As you approach, the lush front yard welcomes you to a cozy, classic house design. Discover a spacious kitchen with a breakfast bar awaiting your creative touch. The 4 BR's can be sleeping spaces, a home office, or a gym.  The master suite ensures serenity with its ensuite bath.  Outside, a refreshing pool and a spacious deck promise endless barbeques and gatherings.
